  (text "Work queue: CAP-FOG. ADR-0021 cable-entry boundary. Contact 1 is SW_COMMON; contacts 2/3 are the independent FOG_A_SW_IN/FOG_B_SW_IN requests. D_FOG1 is the primary protector at the PB entry. R_FOG_GND is fitted for the default dry-contact assembly. R_FOG_12V and F_FOG_12V are mutually exclusive DNP parts for a measured 12 V switch. Do not finalize the loom or manufacturing package before offline switch measurement and routed pulse/return review."
    (at 20 20 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.6 1.6)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "5044ab1c-7be8-551b-9036-684eaec2a29f")
  )
